        <mxCell id="rL3ZQGCBwlLyt4vsJ6vX-165" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;align=left;strokeWidth=1.5;absoluteArcSize=1;" value="&lt;b&gt;Transition Rules&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T1 intake -&amp;gt; clarifying&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Missing critical user information, and tools cannot fill it.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T2 intake -&amp;gt; investigating&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Enough context exists to begin tool calls.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T3 clarifying -&amp;gt; investigating&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; User provides requested information; preserve current budget_mode.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T4 investigating -&amp;gt; resolving&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; confidence &amp;gt;= 0.8.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T5 investigating -&amp;gt; escalating&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; confidence &amp;lt; 0.5.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T6 investigating -&amp;gt; investigating&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; 0.5 &amp;lt;= confidence &amp;lt; 0.8, missing_info_source = tool, and tool budget remains.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T7 investigating -&amp;gt; clarifying&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; 0.5 &amp;lt;= confidence &amp;lt; 0.8, missing_info_source != &quot;tool&quot; &amp;nbsp;OR &amp;nbsp;budget reached&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T8 investigating -&amp;gt; escalating&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Tool limit reached and no safe guidance is available.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T9 investigating -&amp;gt; resolving partial&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Tool limit reached, but safe low-risk guidance exists.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T10 resolving -&amp;gt; closed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; User confirms issue is resolved.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T11 resolving -&amp;gt; investigating retry&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; User says not resolved and resolution_attempts &amp;lt; 2. Use retry budget.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T12 resolving -&amp;gt; clarifying exception&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; resolution_attempts &amp;gt;= 2, user adds a new critical fact, and exception_used = false.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T13 resolving -&amp;gt; escalating&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; resolution_attempts &amp;gt;= 2 and no new critical fact, or exception was already used.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; T14 escalating -&amp;gt; closed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Human IT handoff package is completed.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Runtime Budget Parameters&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; main_tool_budget = 5&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; retry_tool_budget = 3&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; exception_tool_budget = 2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; max_resolution_attempts = 2&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; Exception path can be used once per case. CaseState preserves facts, tool traces, failed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp; resolutions, and budget_mode.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
